{"tid":1362222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢去做地盤","createTime":"2019-07-24T21:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:25:47.000Z","uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df019c82bd5b10eea6a0ff4f0b0c77abd10c0bef","tid":1362222,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T21:30:05.000Z","msg":"認真, 發夢之前做過幾日地盤. 我打機嘅時候發覺勇士們對鞋好似唔夠防護. <br />\n<br />\n我覺得而家佢哋對鞋應該要升級<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kcsgroup.com.hk/brands_01.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kcsgroup.com.hk%2Fbrands_01.php&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=42adbc58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.kcsgroup.com.hk/brands_01.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然有少少重. 但係打機畀前線絕對夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要大家都係黑色認唔出, 既可攻又可守. 玻璃樽都踢爆呀. 打機一定攞第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我冇嘢講</span>"},{"pid":"2ece51d47c03ca06ea96a5b62b35fb4682d742e3","tid":1362222,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:38:40.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"5ddf998a702b6e089e9420461e57e3e1fac24cbd","tid":1362222,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"推"}]}